                     <interp inst="t18220109-81-person792" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was on the spot; I had been watching the prisoner with three others for half an hour, but did not see him at Hurley's.</p>
               <p>(Padlock produced and sworn to.)</p>
